{"tid":963423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛里斯新年願望：「熱」捧冠軍","createTime":"2018-12-31T14:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T18:03:09.000Z","uid":31626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ad3044308a17d2b298585c4f82e57ca4aa864c","tid":963423,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oz1Hacn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOz1Hacn.png&h=c2080704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e4d1a607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】2018即將過去，隊長洛里斯在新一年最希望就即為熱刺贏得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺對上一次捧走錦標，已經是2008年的英聯盃，就算近年進步神速，也未曾染指任何冠軍。今夏為法國奪取世界盃的門將洛里斯（Hugo Lloris）說：「冠軍是我們努力的目標。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們身在英超，有很多競爭對手、強隊、名將，這也是令人感到刺激的地方。我們身在最具競爭性的國家，所以要以同樣的心態作戰，踢出最佳的足球。」洛里斯表示。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺於上場英超主場以1:3不敵狼隊，從次席跌落第3位，現時已經落後榜首的利物浦達9分，洛里斯認為：「我們在過去已證明了熱刺十分有競爭力，正跟最佳的球隊拉近距離。」"},{"pid":"8f504947aa0433bf8a4cdde4002db3c66349f4a9","tid":963423,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d4376ebe9a4e46d02ae3393572ad66b504bf09","tid":963423,"uid":77132,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:35:06.000Z","msg":"入到黎即刻笑咗"},{"pid":"ae5297a18a07b59f859b9cdf3d6195d7e393e338","tid":963423,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"想問唔計聯賽盃，熱同猁對上一次拎冠係幾時？"},{"pid":"6c3fc2ae565ac475860204940c7e7a5c32e47280","tid":963423,"uid":38189,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ae5297a18a07b59f859b9cdf3d6195d7e393e338","tid":963423,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"想問唔計聯賽盃，熱同猁對上一次拎冠係幾時？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:43:12.000Z